# Terminology — Zero Tolerance

**`docs/explanation/terminology.md` is the single source of truth for all identifiers.**

Before writing code, OpenAPI, DB schema, tests, or docs, read the registry.

## Merge blockers

- Typos of registered terms
- Spelling variants (camelCase in JSON where snake_case is registered, etc.)
- New identifiers without a registry row in the same PR

## Common mistakes

| Wrong | Correct (see terminology.md) |
|---|---|
| `contactForm` in JSON | `contact_form` |
| `inquiry` | `submission` |
| `Controller` suffix | `Handler` |
| `Service` suffix | `UseCase` |
| `message` (domain) | `submission` or `submission_note` |
